# Part 1 — Project Phases Overview & Phases 1–2

---

## 1. Project Phases Overview

| Phase | Name | Weeks | Calendar | Goal |
|-------|------|-------|----------|------|
| 1 | Foundation | 1–2 | Weeks 1–2 | Next.js scaffold, Supabase schema, auth, onboarding, design system, app shell |
| 2 | AI Chat Core | 3–5 | Weeks 3–5 | Claude pipeline, chat UI, confirmation cards, real-time updates |
| 3 | Dashboard & Reports | 6–7 | Weeks 6–7 | KPI dashboard, sales/purchase/profit pages, charts |
| 4 | Full CRUD & Contacts | 8–9 | Weeks 8–9 | Products, inventory, transactions, suppliers, customers, settings |
| 5 | Polish, PWA & Launch | 10–12 | Weeks 10–12 | Insights engine, PWA, landing page, testing, deployment, go-live |

**Total estimated build time: 12 weeks** (solo senior dev or agentic AI). Reduce to 8–9 weeks with two devs splitting frontend and backend.

---

## 2. Phase 1 — Foundation (Weeks 1–2)

### Goal
Bootable Next.js app with Supabase schema, authentication, onboarding wizard, design system, and app shell (sidebar, layout, route protection). No feature screens yet — but every screen that follows has a home.

---

