Flow: Owner → Settings → Team → Invite → enters email + role → API creates `invitations` row → sends email with link `{APP_URL}/invite/{token}` → recipient clicks → if authenticated, `business_members` row created, redirect to `/app/chat`. If not authenticated, redirect to `/signup?invite={token}`, post-signup auto-accepts.

