**Testing checkpoint — Phase 1 done when:**
- [ ] `npm run dev` boots without errors
- [ ] Supabase migrations apply cleanly
- [ ] Sign up creates auth user + redirects to `/onboarding`
- [ ] Onboarding completes and creates business + member + location
- [ ] Sign in redirects to `/app/chat`
- [ ] Unauthenticated users redirected to `/signin`
- [ ] Sidebar renders with all nav items
- [ ] Mobile bottom nav renders on small screens
- [ ] All route stubs are reachable
- [ ] Invitation flow: create invite → accept → new member appears

**Common failure points:**
- Supabase RLS blocks INSERT on `businesses` during onboarding — fix: the INSERT policy on `businesses` must allow any authenticated user to create
- Middleware redirect loop — fix: ensure `/onboarding` is in the authenticated-but-no-business-yet allow list
- Cookie not set on SSR — fix: use `@supabase/ssr` `createServerClient` correctly with `cookies()` from `next/headers`

